Sisulu has accompanied South African President, Cyril Ramaphosa, who is attending the 25th Commonwealth Heads of Government Meeting (CHOGM) that takes place on Thursday and Friday. Finance Minister, Nhlanhla Nene, and Trade and Industry Minister, Dr. Rob Davies, have also travelled with Ramaphosa. Their message to the CHOGM is that "South Africa is open for business and is an investment destination of choice".

--ANA--